data.description: Wonderful home in the heart of Siloam, this home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, an oversized lot at the end of a cul-de-sac. The deck in the back allows you to have serenity right at home gazing into the treetops! Inside you will find a split floor plan, one level, with granite countertops, formal dining along with a small intimate area off the kitchen, laundry connects to the 2-car garage, the lot extends to the side of the home adding lots of extra yard space. Great option for any family looking for a wonderful option in Siloam! By appointment only!
